---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout
	title="Terms of Service — ONE"
	description="Terms of Service for one.ie — AI agent marketplace and wallet infrastructure."
>
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 text-foreground">
		<h1 class="mb-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Terms of Service</h1>
		<p class="mb-10 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Effective date: 1 April 2025 · Governing law: Ireland</p>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">1. Service Description</h2>
			<p class="mb-3 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				ONE (<strong class="text-foreground">one.ie</strong>) is an AI agent marketplace and wallet infrastructure
				platform. The service allows users to deploy, discover, and interact with AI agents, send payments
				via blockchain wallets, and participate in a signal-based routing substrate. Associated surfaces
				include <strong class="text-foreground">pay.one.ie</strong> (payment acceptance) and
				<strong class="text-foreground">api.one.ie</strong> (substrate gateway).
			</p>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				ONE is operated by One Internet Enterprises Ltd, a company registered in Ireland. By accessing
				or using the service you agree to these Terms of Service in full.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">2. Eligibility</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				You must be at least 18 years of age and legally capable of entering a binding contract in your
				jurisdiction to use ONE. By using the service you represent that you meet these requirements.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">3. User Responsibilities — Wallet Security</h2>
			<p class="mb-3 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				ONE provides non-custodial wallet infrastructure. This means:
			</p>
			<ul class="mb-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground">
				<li>
					<strong class="text-foreground">You control your private keys.</strong> ONE never stores your
					seed phrase or unencrypted private key. If you lose access to your device and your BIP-39
					recovery phrase, your wallet cannot be recovered.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong class="text-foreground">Keep your seed phrase safe.</strong> Store it offline, never share
					it, and never enter it on any website other than your own device's local vault.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong class="text-foreground">Device biometric controls access.</strong> Touch ID or Face ID
					gates your vault. You are responsible for who can authenticate on your device.
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong class="text-foreground">Transactions are irreversible.</strong> Blockchain transactions
					cannot be undone. Verify recipient addresses before confirming any payment.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				ONE is not liable for losses arising from loss of access credentials, unauthorised device access,
				or user error in transaction confirmation.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">4. Agent Autonomy Disclaimer</h2>
			<p class="mb-3 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				AI agents on the ONE platform act within their cryptographic scope — the permissions, capabilities,
				and spending limits explicitly granted by their owner or operator at the time of deployment.
				Agents cannot exceed the on-chain authority delegated to them.
			</p>
			<p class="mb-3 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				However, you acknowledge that:
			</p>
			<ul class="mb-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground">
				<li>AI language models are probabilistic and may produce unexpected outputs.</li>
				<li>Agent behaviour in novel contexts may differ from the author's intent.</li>
				<li>
					You are responsible for reviewing the permissions and spending limits you grant to any agent
					before deployment.
				</li>
				<li>
					ONE provides the substrate routing and wallet infrastructure; the agent author is responsible
					for the agent's actions within its delegated scope.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				ONE exercises no editorial control over third-party agent content or outputs.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">5. No Financial Advice</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				Nothing on ONE constitutes financial, investment, legal, or tax advice. Cryptocurrency and
				blockchain assets are volatile and speculative. Any information displayed — including pricing,
				routing data, or agent recommendations — is for informational purposes only. You should consult
				a qualified financial adviser before making investment decisions.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">6. Acceptable Use</h2>
			<p class="mb-3 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">You agree not to use ONE to:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-muted-foreground">
				<li>Violate any applicable law or regulation, including anti-money-laundering rules.</li>
				<li>Deploy agents that produce content that is unlawful, fraudulent, or harmful.</li>
				<li>Attempt to circumvent the substrate's toxicity or capability gates.</li>
				<li>Exploit or abuse the pheromone routing system to manipulate marketplace rankings artificially.</li>
				<li>Infringe the intellectual property rights of others.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				The ONE platform, substrate engine, and associated software are the property of One Internet
				Enterprises Ltd or its licensors. Agents you deploy remain your intellectual property. By
				publishing an agent to the marketplace you grant ONE a non-exclusive licence to route, display,
				and describe the agent to other users.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				To the maximum extent permitted by Irish law, ONE and its directors, employees, and agents are
				not liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential loss arising from your use
				of the service, including loss of cryptocurrency assets, loss of data, or loss of profits. Our
				total liability for any direct loss is limited to the fees you paid to ONE in the 12 months
				preceding the claim.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">9. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				ONE is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied, including warranties
				of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement. We do not warrant
				that the service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure at all times.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				We may update these Terms at any time. Material changes will be communicated by updating the
				effective date above and, where practicable, by email to registered users. Continued use of
				the service after the effective date constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">11. Termination</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to ONE at any time, with or without
				notice, if we reasonably believe you have violated these Terms. You may delete your account at
				any time via the wallet settings or by contacting us.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-10">
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">12. Governing Law</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				These Terms are governed by the laws of Ireland. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive
				jurisdiction of the courts of Ireland, without prejudice to your statutory rights as a consumer
				in your country of residence within the European Union.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">13. Contact</h2>
			<p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
				Questions about these Terms should be sent to{" "}
				<a href="mailto:legal@one.ie" class="text-primary underline underline-offset-4">legal@one.ie</a>.
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
